    "During pre-training, the model, by definition, will not be able to predict the statistically most likely word to follow a certain sentence.",
    "Errors in prediction are spotted and then the correct result is fed into the LLM, so that it may learn.",
    "This operation is done millions of times during the pre-training phase.",
    "In addition, these LLMs are capable of performing self-supervised learning, which dispenses with human oversight during pre-training and seems to have proven to be even more effective than human-supervised training.",
